  "text": "Polymerase activity assays were performed following a previously described protocol [CITATION_1] with minor modifications. Briefly, reaction mixtures containing 1 μg of purified TaV pol and TaV rORF1 wild type or variants (Fig 1) , were prepared in 40 μl of transcription buffer (50 mM MES pH 6.0, 100 mM NaCl, 5 mM MgCl 2 , 10% glycerol, 1 mM DTT, 1 mM rATP, rGTP and rCTP, 0.02 mM rUTP, 20 units of RNasin, and 10 μCi [α-",
